src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNo0t4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNo0t4E.jpg&h=7dc743e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個 staff 諗住寫 top/crush 但我係個轆爛呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果喺我不斷煩佢改佢就開左上面果張圖叫我自己揀點形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然衰開有梗路架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞撚完個喼過埋海關出到去 (啲關員棟喺度掛住吹水彩撚你都傻)<br />\n<strong>屌</strong><br />\n個guide呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講撚哂話機場見順便傾埋之後行程人影都冇撚個想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺度補充下: 話説我上次嚟almaty唔係自己搞, 臨走攞左個guide既contact今次請返佢費事煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次嚟去左玩差館巴打有興趣再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就上左樓上買sim card, Beeline係必然之選2500kzt 一個月8gb 加內網任打 抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計返$50港紙佢幫你set晒俾錢然後用就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果個guide話塞車我買哂過左4個字先到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmVBMW7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmVBMW7.jpg&h=6cb52bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁中亞揸車簡直係香港十倍加強版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 閘車鳩cut乜到齊 交通如果係返放工係塞撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71f537605e7db978835aff45cd5695c735a5fa7","tid":1174263,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"巴打帶咩機去<br />\n啲相好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b960b0c1e259e7cb21db112f90f73c0db9d4e6","tid