ata-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTVFQ8Z.jpg&h=9fff8024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住落黎啲包同餅都okay係凍咗啲但係味道經過啱啱折磨之後覺得唔錯 野飲有驚喜下圖罐mojito係佢唯一既soft drink 味道唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cekZnfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcekZnfM.jpg&h=27c02110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落左機轉頭再打, 佢個機場好撚顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊著仲有去旅行社見老細嘅笑柒死人故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465ed90d25d431bb1f14a9421c425a70063ad890","tid":1174263,"uid":237901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4fd6163764bae3d2703756f42e49adf017ee25","tid":1174263,"uid":158166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddbe501de2b61fa98dc868adadde083367ca6be6","tid":1174263,"uid":632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63d2d779b35089d509789043c4f21c7ffaac9cd7","tid":1174263,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"song kul 必去<br />\n全個吉國最正既行程（仲正過alako)<br />\n上年300usd /2人 <br />\n3日2夜<br />\n完全斷電斷網 但一d都唔悶 勁享受d景"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHSHYj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHSHYj1.png&h=f7a140d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rntj0yn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRntj0yn.png&h=7ef65410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmocA6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmocA6K.png&h=ddc85ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個湖反而無咩特別 但途中d景真心靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h